node.text: MY BEEF THIS MORNING: Was I SERIOUSLY the only meme account that took the stance against Steve from Blue’s Clues?! WHERE WERE YALL ON THAT?! Straight up left me all alone 😂😂 (meme credit @thetinderblog )

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kevin Flynn in University of South Florida. May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'was at Walmart tonight & saw this man w/ a cart full of stuffed animals. When I asked him why, my heart became full. He told me that every year he dresses up as Santa & walks the halls of the children S ER & resells them to dying kids at a massive markup'.

node.text: It’s still so funny to me when people talk shit to me when the Bucs have a close game. WE WERE THE WORST TEAM EVER FOR LITERALLY 20 YEARS. If y’all really want to talk shit, my college team (USF) is going to get absolutely destroyed tomorrow by UF. They seriously may put up 100 on us. WHAT MAKES IT WORSE is that I’m literally @floridaman and I had every college in Florida sending me promo shit and inviting me to tailgates/giving me free tickets, so last year I made a pledge to support every college in Florida. SO I HAVE TO WATCH UF POUND MY SCHOOL AND BE HAPPY ABOUT IT. On 9/11. Like they’re doing it for America. They’re literally wearing American flags on their helmets as they just decimate my school. ANYWAY, this meme didn’t originally say this lol. I posted it a couple years ago and the guy in the pic talked to me. He is actually cool as fuck. Looks great in jeans. I’d let him taste it.

node.text: Ive taken my bows. And my curtain calls. You’ve brought me fame and fortune andeverythingthatgoeswithit. I thank you all. But it’s been no bed of roses. No pleasure cruise. I consider it a challenge before the human race, and I’d never lose (and it goes on and on and on) WEEEEEEE ARE THE CHAMPIONS, MY FRIEEEEND. AND WE’LL KEEP ON FIGHTIIIIING TILL THE END. WE ARE THE CHAMPIONS, WE ARE THE CHAMPIOOOOONS, NOOOOO TIME FOR LOOOOSERS CAUSE WE WRE THE CHAMPIOOOOONS, OF THE WORLD
